          "type": "Text",
          "format": "html",
          "text": [
            "<p>Amber’s mother suggested that Amber could use the ideas of “in the black” or “in the red” to model addition and subtraction of integers using red and black chips. Amber’s mother gives the following example. </p><ul><li>Tate owes his sister $6 for helping him cut the lawn. He earns $4 watering a neighbor’s plants.</li></ul>"
